at long-term relationship became something more.<\/p>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"780\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-1024x780.jpg\" alt=\"Kevin Costner and Christine Baumgartner in 2022.\" class=\"wp-image-494185\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-1024x780.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-300x229.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-768x585.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-1536x1170.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-2048x1560.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-735x560.jpg 735w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-335x255.jpg 335w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-347x264.jpg 347w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-520x396.jpg 520w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-640x488.jpg 640w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-960x731.jpg 960w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-1080x823.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px\"><\/noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"780\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-1024x780.jpg\" alt=\"Kevin Costner and Christine Baumgartner in 2022.\" class=\"wp-image-494185 lazyload\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-1024x780.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-300x229.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-768x585.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-1536x1170.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-2048x1560.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-735x560.jpg 735w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-335x255.jpg 335w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-347x264.jpg 347w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-520x396.jpg 520w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-640x488.jpg 640w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-960x731.jpg 960w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-1080x823.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px\" data-pin-media=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_02-scaled.jpg\" data-trellis-processed=\"1\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Christine Baumgartner and Kevin Costner attend the 94th Annual Academy Awards at Hollywood and Highland on March 27, 2022.<span class=\"image-caption-credit\"> (Photo Credit: David Livingston\/Getty Images)<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>On September 25 of 2004, Costner and Baumgartner had a beautiful and picturesque wedding on The Dunbar. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The 160-acre ranch, which shares a name with Costner&rsquo;s <em>Dances with Wolves <\/em>character, remains a Costner-owned private wedding venue to this day. Though of course <a href=\"https:\/\/www.thehollywoodgossip.com\/2024\/02\/who-is-abbey-lee\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Costner continues to be a working actor<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Three years after they married, they welcomed their first child, Cayden Wyatt. Costner and Baumgartner also share Hayes Logan and Grace Avery.<\/p>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"688\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_03-1024x688.jpg\" alt=\"Kevin Costner and Christine Baumgartner at the SAG Awards in 2022.\" class=\"wp-image-494186\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_03-1024x688.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_03-300x201.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_03-768x516.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_03-1536x1031.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_03-2048x1375.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_03-735x494.jpg 735w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_03-335x225.jpg 335w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_03-347x233.jpg 347w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_03-520x349.jpg 520w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_03-640x430.jpg 640w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_03-960x645.jpg 960w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_03-1080x725.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px\"><\/noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"688\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_03-1024x688.jpg\" alt=\"Kevin Costner and Christine Baumgartner at the SAG Awards in 2022.\" class=\"wp-image