rences.&rdquo; Costner&rsquo;s attorney would later accuse her of planning the divorce in advance, citing a vehicle purchase.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It was not an amicable split. After nearly two decades of marriage, they had the two have their shared children, a lot of property (including their marital home in Santa Barbara), and clearly a lot of hurt feelings.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Baumgartner was aiming to be the latest of Kevin Costner&rsquo;s ex-wives. One particularly eye-catching point of contention was the matter of child-support payments.<\/p>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"694\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_04-1024x694.jpg\" alt=\"Kevin Costner and ex-wife Christine Baumgartner in happier times.\" class=\"wp-image-494187\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_04-1024x694.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_04-300x203.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_04-768x520.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_04-1536x1041.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_04-2048x1387.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_04-735x498.jpg 735w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_04-335x227.jpg 335w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_04-347x235.jpg 347w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_04-520x352.jpg 520w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_04-640x434.jpg 640w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_04-960x650.jpg 960w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/0