"> (Photo Credit: Frazer Harrison\/Getty Images for Paramount Network)<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In June of 2023, the world learned that Baumgartner had requested $248,000 per month in child-support payments, in order to maintain the accustomed lifestyle of all three kids while they&rsquo;re with their mother.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Costner&rsquo;s proposal was that he pay $38,000 per month. Ultimately, the court did not agree with either.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In September of 2023, the court ordered Costner to pay Baumgartner $63,209 each month in child-support.<\/p>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"670\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-1024x670.jpg\" alt=\"Kevin Costner and his ex-wife, Christine Baumgartner, in 2015.\" class=\"wp-image-494188\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-1024x670.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-300x196.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-768x503.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-1536x1006.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-2048x1341.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-735x481.jpg 735w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-335x219.jpg 335w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-347x227.jpg 347w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-520x340.jpg 520w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-640x419.jpg 640w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-960x628.jpg 960w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-1080x707.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px\"><\/noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"670\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-1024x670.jpg\" alt=\"Kevin Costner and his ex-wife, Christine Baumgartner, in 2015.\" class=\"wp-image-494188 lazyload\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-1024x670.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-300x196.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-768x503.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-1536x1006.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-2048x1341.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-735x481.jpg 735w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-335x219.jpg 335w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-347x227.jpg 347w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-520x340.jpg 520w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-640x419.jpg 640w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-960x628.jpg 960w, https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-1080x707.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 760px) calc(100vw - 20px), 720px\" data-pin-media=\"https:\/\/cdn.thehollywoodgossip.com\/uploads\/2024\/02\/0226_kevincostner_05-scaled.jpg\" data-trellis-processed=\"1\"><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Kevin Costner and Christine Baumgartner attend the world premiere of Disney&rsquo;s &lsquo;McFarland, USA&rsquo; at the El Capitan Theatre, February 9, 2015.<span cla